// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1009 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: cbfcbf2b-eb55-59d3-8ef4-c29c16a3ea25

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:10* OR ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
